7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both JetBrains AI and Replit AI share a solid foundation of core features including Autocomplete, Code Generation, Debugging, Multi Language. Where JetBrains AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Refactoring and Test Generation and Ide Integration and Documentation, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, JetBrains AI holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Replit AI scores 7/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, JetBrains AI offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $10/mo, compared to Replit AI's starting price of $25/mo. Replit AI stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. JetBrains AI requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
